Module qilletni.api
Package dev.qilletni.api.lang.types

Interface CollectionType

All Superinterfaces:
AnyType, QilletniType
public non-sealed interface CollectionType extends AnyType
Represents a collection type in Qilletni. This is essentially an abstracted playlist, or list of songs. This may be created by the "Collection Name" collection by "Creator Name" expression syntax.

    • getCollectionDefinition

      CollectionDefinition getCollectionDefinition()
      Retrieves the current collection definition associated with the implementing object. The collection definition determines how the collection data is classified or resolved, such as by URL, name and creator, prepopulated data, or a list of specific songs.
      Returns:
      The CollectionDefinition representing the current method of collection classification or resolution
